    <subsection label="iso">
      <content lang="en" title="GeeXboX ISO">
        We're currently releasing 2 versions of the GeeXboX : French and English. The installer software includes the original ISO, increasing the size slightly. It's now up to you to choose the menu's langage that fits you best :<br/><br/>
          * <b><use name="dl-iso-en"/> - <use name="dl1-iso-en"/> - <use name="dl2-iso-en"/> - <use name="dl3-iso-en"/> - 6.2 MB</b><br/>
          * <b><use name="dl-iso-fr"/> - <use name="dl1-iso-fr"/> - <use name="dl2-iso-fr"/> - <use name="dl3-iso-fr"/> - 6.2 MB</b><br/>
          <br/>

          * <use name="dl-old-en"/> - <use name="dl1-old"/> - <use name="dl2-old"/> - <use name="dl3-old"/><br/>
          * <b><use name="dl-md5"/></b><br/>
      </content>
